==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: After-image
<hw>Aft"er-im`age</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The impression
of a vivid sensation retained by the retina of the eye after the cause
has been removed; also extended to impressions left of tones, smells,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Afterings</ent>⟦br⟧
